        <h1>Monitoring: basic concepts</h1>
        <p>PlantVisorPRO Locale lets use monitor a system in different ways:</p>
        <table style="border-left-style: Solid;border-top-style: Solid;border-right-style: Solid;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-left-width: 2px;border-right-width: 2px;border-top-width: 2px;border-bottom-width: 2px;border-left-color: #5f5f5f;border-right-color: #5f5f5f;border-top-color: #5f5f5f;border-bottom-color: #5f5f5f;width: 100%;border-spacing: 0px;border-spacing: 0px;" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
            <col style="width: 50.001%;" />
            <col style="width: 50.001%;" />
            <tr valign="top">
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 50.001%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #eaeaea;border-right-width: 3px;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-top-width: 3px;border-top-color: #ffffff;border-top-style: Solid;border-left-color: #ffffff;border-left-style: Solid;border-left-width: 3px;" bgcolor="#EAEAEA" width="50.001%">
                    <p>See menu <span style="font-weight: bold;">Plant, <span style="font-weight: bold;">Global</span></span></p>
                    <p>See menu <span style="font-weight: bold;">Site, Global, &lt;groupName&gt;</span></p>
                    <p>
                        <img src="../Resources/Images/MonitoraggioGlobale350px.png" style="border: none;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;width: 366px;height: 164px;" width="366" height="164" border="0" />
                    </p>
                </td>
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 50.001%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #eaeaea;border-right-width: 3px;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-top-width: 3px;border-top-color: #ffffff;border-top-style: Solid;" bgcolor="#EAEAEA" width="50.001%">
                    <p>In these functions the user can:</p>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>check alarms</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="2">
                            <p>set group parameters</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="3">
                            <p>check HACCP and log graphs</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="4">
                            <p>open device details</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top">
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 50.001%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #eaeaea;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-width: 3px;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;border-left-style: Solid;border-left-color: #ffffff;" bgcolor="#EAEAEA" width="50.001%">
                    <p>See menu <span style="font-weight: bold;">Plant</span><span style="font-weight: bold;">Global</span><span>, device details</span></p>
                    <p>See menu <span style="font-weight: bold;">Plant, Global, &lt;groupName&gt;</span>, device detail</p>
                    <p>
                        <img src="../Resources/Images/monitoraggioDispositivo350px.png" style="border: none;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;width: 366px;height: 200px;" width="366" height="200" border="0" />
                    </p>
                </td>
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 50.001%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #eaeaea;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-width: 3px;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;" bgcolor="#EAEAEA" width="50.001%">
                    <p>In this function the user can:</p>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>check status, probes, I/O variables</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="2">
                            <p>set parameters</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="3">
                            <p>check HACCP and log graphs</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top">
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 50.001%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #eaeaea;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-width: 3px;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;border-left-style: Solid;border-left-color: #ffffff;" bgcolor="#EAEAEA" width="50.001%">
                    <p>See menu <span style="font-weight: bold;">Plant</span>, <span style="font-weight: bold;">Devices</span></p>
                    <p>
                        <img src="../Resources/Images/mappa_tabella_350px.png" style="border: none;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;width: 366px;height: 146px;" width="366" height="146" border="0" />
                    </p>
                </td>
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 50.001%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #eaeaea;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-width: 3px;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;" bgcolor="#EAEAEA" width="50.001%">
                    <p>In this function, for each device the user can:</p>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>check status and probes</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="2">
                            <p>check HACCP and log graphs</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="3">
                            <p>open device details</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top">
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 50.001%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #eaeaea;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-width: 3px;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;border-left-style: Solid;border-left-color: #ffffff;" bgcolor="#EAEAEA" width="50.001%">
                    <p>See menu <span style="font-weight: bold;">Plant</span>, <span style="font-weight: bold;">Map</span></p>
                    <p style="font-weight: bold;">
                        <img src="../Resources/Images/mappa_sinottica_350px_350x242.png" style="border: none;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;width: 350;height: 242;" border="0" />
                    </p>
                </td>
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 50.001%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #eaeaea;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-width: 3px;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;" bgcolor="#EAEAEA" width="50.001%">
                    <p>Map structure and aspect depend on installers. Usually, there is a main map used to navigate to detail maps like a website.</p>
                    <p>In this function, for each device the user can:</p>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>check and edit status and variables</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <h2>Data acquisition</h2>
        <p>PlantVisorPRO Locale acquires data at a set interval. Log data is recorded based at set periods (for variables that follow HACCP regulations).  Log recording is set by the user. See the <a href="PVPRO-locale__scheda_tecnica.htm">Technical sheet</a>. See chapter <a href="Report__concetti_di_base.htm">Report: basic concepts</a></p>
